{"tid":862762,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[買美股]  TD, CS, Firstrade 邊間好？","createTime":"2018-10-15T05:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T00:22:47.000Z","uid":73883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"3deff2160b471af958e26edd89a7d35744866e3b","tid":862762,"uid":73883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:30:15.000Z","msg":"未買過美股，想開戶買下 ETF，睇長線。<br />\n<br />\n做左少少功課，呢幾間都有 SIPC。<br />\n<br />\n睇返大半年前有人話 TD 一定要開香港 TD 戶口，而香港戶口買唔到 ETF，唔知而家仲係咪咁？<br />\n<br />\nCS 好似唔錯，但要擺 25k 美金...有少少卻步。<br />\n<br />\nFirstrade 有好多優惠，但好似好少人講，規模都比較細，係咪靠得住？<br />\n<br />\n又有無人知網頁介面嚟講，邊間比較好用？<br />\n<br />\n唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2473f77964b50e24db6639b52ac685671cdf0462","tid":862762,"uid":30347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:33:00.000Z","msg":"我用美國TD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c489d21baacdc92eb3a8d304d59bbab9161dce","tid":862762,"uid":138593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2473f77964b50e24db6639b52ac685671cdf0462","tid":862762,"uid":30347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:33:00.000Z","msg":"我用美國TD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:34:40.000Z","msg":"好似要美國戶口？"},{"pid":"4baa0a4ea602934f2057061b05be26d14fe76dac","tid":862762,"uid":66839,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:35:22.000Z","msg":"牛牛"},{"pid":"8dcb71aea7b2ce1765dae59d19552d61e72204d5","tid":862762,"uid":90304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:36:01.000Z","msg":"IB"},{"pid":"0af5bcc849fd72d42b604e7aefb3da6bed296cba","tid":862762,"uid":73883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8dcb71aea7b2ce1765dae59d19552d61e7